Subject: [PATCH 2/5] Update img2tyles to use Python 3

This patch was originally introduced in the upstream BlastEm Mercurial
repository to update the img2tiles script for Python 3 compatibility.

It was subsequently extracted and modified by Mingcong Bai to adapt to
our version of source code (v0.6.2).

This commit regenerates the previously existing diff into a standard
Git patch format. This is done to ensure structural consistency across
patch series.

Original Author: Mike Pavone <pavone@retrodev.com>
Origin: https://www.retrodev.com/repos/blastem/rev/dbbf0100f249
Upstream-Status: Backport (Modified)

[Mingcong Bai: extracted and modified the upstream patch]
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
[CyberNeko-AI: regenerated patch from raw diff]
Signed-off-by: CyberNeko-AI <cyberneko.ai@aosc.io>

---
